OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves confirmed
OL,7,Fhuge cuts to benefits in her Spring
OL,8,FStatement on Wednesday, and went even
OL,9,Ffurther by freezing the health element
OL,10,Fof universal credit to save extra cash.
OL,12,FWhen the package of benefits cuts was
OL,13,Fannounced last week, the government
OL,14,Fsaid they were waiting to publish
OL,15,Fdetails on how many people were
OL,16,Fimpacted until the Spring Statement.
