OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FCritics have accused the government of
OL,7,Ftrying to "bury bad news," as the
OL,8,Ffigures show the cuts will hit
OL,9,Fmillions of vulnerable families and
OL,10,Fdisabled people.
OL,12,FThe government estimates that in 2029-
OL,13,F30, 3.2 million families will lose an
OL,14,Faverage of #1,720 a year as a result
OL,15,Fof the cuts, with 250,000 people
OL,16,Fpushed into relative poverty.
